  "remarks": "JSC Holography Industry is the leading Belarusian producer of protective holograms and crystallograms. Under Belarusian legislation, protective holographic stickers are put on excise stamps, including excise stamps on alcoholic beverages, a wide range of consumer goods, cash registers and slot machines. This creates significant demand for JSC Holography Industry’s products.",
